{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.680", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.400", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr verehrte Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.760", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Minister! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.640", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Deutschland herrscht Notstand\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.000", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Pflegenotstand in Pflegeheimen und Krankenh\u00e4usern und offensichtlich auch Notstand im Gesundheitsministerium mit einem Minister, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.520", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der lieber Hartz-IV-Empf\u00e4nger diskreditiert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.680", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "statt diesen Pflegenotstand zu beenden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.400", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das hat gravierende Folgen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.560", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erstens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.040", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Menschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.320", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Pflege ben\u00f6tigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.160", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "fehlt es h\u00e4ufig an menschlicher Zuwendung und an ausreichender Hygiene. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.400", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist doch skandal\u00f6s, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.560", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Patienten nur einmal in der Woche gewaschen werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.800", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es fehlt an Pflegequalit\u00e4t, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.000", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die die W\u00fcrde der Menschen bewahrt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.400", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zweitens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.040", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine Pflegkraft muss in deutschen Krankenh\u00e4usern bis zu 19\u00a0Patienten versorgen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.840", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deutschland ist im europ\u00e4ischen Vergleich absolutes Schlusslicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.360", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "K\u00f6rperliche und seelische \u00dcberlastungen bestimmen den Tagesablauf der Pflegekr\u00e4fte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.360", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Kolleginnen und Kollegen k\u00f6nnen nicht mehr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.600", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch wenn sie wollen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.520", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das bei einem viel zu geringen Lohn."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.160", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Drittens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.240", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr die Angeh\u00f6rigen hei\u00dft das: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.960", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Pflege macht arm. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.600", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Kosten explodieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.880", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "beispielsweise bei den Eigenanteilen f\u00fcr das Pflegeheim. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.360", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Viele Familien k\u00f6nnen die finanzielle Belastung nicht mehr stemmen und m\u00fcssen Hilfe zur Pflege, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.800", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "also Sozialhilfe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.280", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in Anspruch nehmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.240", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist doch eine Schande in einem der reichsten L\u00e4nder dieser Erde."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.400", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gesundheit ist zur Ware verkommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.640", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit der m\u00f6glichst viel Profit erwirtschaftet werden soll; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.320", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist das Problem. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.960", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sieht man auch daran, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.640", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sich die Preise f\u00fcr Arzneimittel in den letzten zehn Jahren vervierfacht haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.040", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dringend ben\u00f6tigte Medikamente werden zu Luxusartikeln. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "111.320", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr Pharmakonzerne ist das die Lizenz zum Gelddrucken. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "111.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.400", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Pflegeheime werden an Finanzinvestoren verscherbelt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.720", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Krankenh\u00e4user werden zu Profitunternehmen umgebaut. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.640", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Beispielsweise hat Helios allein im vergangenen Jahr \u00fcber 1\u00a0Milliarde Euro Gewinn vor Steuern gemacht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.600", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sind Profite, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.920", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die auf dem R\u00fccken der Menschen gemacht werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.600", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.800", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist Geld, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.920", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das dem Gesundheitssystem und der Pflege fehlt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.760", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Minister, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.760", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben offensichtlich nicht vor, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.920", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "daran etwas zu \u00e4ndern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.480", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dass die 8\u00a0000\u00a0zus\u00e4tzlichen Pflegkr\u00e4fte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.560", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie im Koalitionsvertrag vorgesehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.320", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht ausreichen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.960", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "haben offensichtlich selbst Sie erkannt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.960", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben jetzt eine Pflegekraft pro Pflegeeinrichtung angek\u00fcndigt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.720", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das reicht aber bei weitem nicht aus. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.960", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kollege Lauterbach hat von 50\u00a0000 bis 100\u00a0000 gesprochen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.520", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Kosten daf\u00fcr wollen Sie wahrscheinlich wieder den Menschen aufb\u00fcrden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.240", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sind nicht bereit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.520", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "strukturell etwas zu ver\u00e4ndern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.320", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen werden Sie in der Pflege weiterhin nur hom\u00f6opathische Globuli verteilen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.800", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "statt dem System endlich eine ordentliche Therapie zu verordnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.760", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Am Tag der Pflege gab es \u00fcber 300\u00a0Aktionen von vielen Initiativen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.280", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die uns Abgeordnete aufgefordert haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.640", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "endlich zu handeln. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.240", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie lange wollen Sie die noch ignorieren? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.760", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir Linke verschaffen diesen Stimmen in diesem Haus Geh\u00f6r."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.640", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen eine qualitativ gute und bezahlbare Pflege, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.040", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die den Menschen ihre Lebensw\u00fcrde erh\u00e4lt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.040", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar mit guten Arbeitsbedingungen f\u00fcr die Besch\u00e4ftigten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.880", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daf\u00fcr brauchen wir einen gesetzlichen Personalschl\u00fcssel f\u00fcr alle Bereiche in der Pflege, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.920", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine solidarische B\u00fcrgerversicherung sowie einen Pflegemindestlohn von 14,50\u00a0Euro in der Altenpflege und einen Tarifvertrag, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.320", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der f\u00fcr alle Pflegekr\u00e4fte gilt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.640", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "An dieser Stelle m\u00f6chte ich solidarische Gr\u00fc\u00dfe an die Kolleginnen und Kollegen von Vivantes schicken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "234.000", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die f\u00fcr einen solchen Tarifvertrag heute hier in Berlin streiken."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "234.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.000", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.000", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die n\u00e4chste Rednerin ist die Kollegin Kordula Schulz-Asche f\u00fcr B\u00fcndnis\u00a090/Die Gr\u00fcnen."
   ]
  }
 ]
}